    <h2>Common Questions</h2>
    <dl class="faq">
      <dt>Q: Does this send real fake messages to people?</dt>
      <dd>A: No—EscapePing only delivers a notification &amp; message to <em>you</em>, so you can gracefully exit an awkward situation.</dd>

      <dt>Q: Is Premium worth it?</dt>
      <dd>A: Absolutely. Premium unlocks your phone-type theme (iOS/Android), lets you write custom messages, and includes three times as many quick-send templates.</dd>

      <dt>Q: Why didn’t I get a notification?</dt>
      <dd>A: If you’ve force-closed the app (swiping it away), background delivery can’t work. We recommend leaving EscapePing running in the background so your notification always comes through.</dd>
    </dl>

